&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AXON&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AXON is a global healthcare communications agency that ignites change in healthcare. Through the power of life-changing communications, we contribute to medical advances that improve lives. At the core of every scientific innovation and advancement, there is a simple and compelling story to be told. We know how to tell that story, how to use the right tools to reach the right audiences at the right time, to provoke meaningful change.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We specialise in advising clients on medical affairs, clinical studies, real-world evidence, marketing, advocacy, and communications, all underpinned by insights and creative strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AXON has an international reach, with offices in Copenhagen, London, New York, and Toronto, and a worldwide affiliate network. Established in 2002, we have a deep heritage and expertise in healthcare strategy and communication, and we continue to learn and grow in the fast-changing healthcare sphere. AXON is proudly an AVENIR GLOBAL company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Creative Marketing at AXON is all about doing the right thing.&amp;nbsp;We believe that’s about honest consultation with clients, so we act in their interests but not always according to their brief. Insightful consideration to unlock more value. And pushing creativity upstream to give it more clout. All this gives us confidence in what we deliver and builds confidence in us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Creative Marketing is the newest practice in AXON, so we have the rare opportunity to build and shape the practice just the way we want to. We’re looking for a like-minded Senior Designer/Video who is set up for the challenge and genuinely interested in the experience of building our practice and with the support of their team, driving their client accounts and projects. Joining the Creative Marketing team at AXON will give team members at all levels opportunities they may not experience in a mainstream healthcare marketing agency – including opportunities to work with practices outside of creative marketing, working on Global/European accounts and internal responsibilities that help shape the direction of our practice. If you’re an ambitious Senior Designer/Video looking for a new opportunity to push yourself and your career to that next step, we would love to hear from you. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Designer/Video at AXON, you will work closely with the Senior Art Director and wider creative team to elevate every project from concept to final delivery across design, video and motion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will bring senior-level creative craft, strong visual judgement, and hands-on video editing and development capability, helping shape compelling work across campaigns, digital channels, events, pitches, social content and client communications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role requires someone who thrives in a fast-moving, collaborative environment and takes pride in delivering beautifully crafted, strategically considered work across static, digital, film and animated formats. The successful candidate will be passionate about creative excellence, eager to push ideas further, and enthusiastic about embracing new technologies and creative approaches.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates must demonstrate strong conceptual thinking, exceptional attention to detail, advanced design and video craft skills, and the ability to confidently communicate and present creative ideas to stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
